title: #92Noon looking forward to year 2 for Kirk Cousins
description: After Kirk Cousins joined the Powertrip morning show on Wednesday, 92noon discussed looking forward to his 2nd year with the squad, the fanbases perception, took phone calls on whether or not to be "all-in" on him into the 2019 season
